title: RunPhones Wireless
description:
Finally, there is a comfortable and safe listening solution for exercise enthusiasts that don’t include painful ear buds that constantly fall out.  RunPhones headphones are the world’s most secure headphones for running and exercising.  The product’s innovative, over the ear design features ultra-slim headphones embedded inside of a sporty, moisture-wicking, machine-washable headband.

Questions?  Please contact our Customer Service Representatives at Service@AcousticSheep.com or call 877-838-4790.  Happy Running!
